    ####  Current Version - 1.2.1 - 2015.03.29

    * Fix Autocompletion when using IPython3 [#1351](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1351).
 
    ####  1.2 - 2015.03.27

    * Support Scala and Java, including sharing classes with Groovy.
    * Support running Python2 and Python3 at the same time, even with different versions of IPython [#776](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/776).
    * Allow user to select location of language backend from their beaker.prefs.json file, as well as the options passed to it [#1166](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1166).
    * Works with IPython3 (in addtion to 1 and 2) [#1222](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1222).
    * Works with Mac OS 10.6 and 10.7 [#408](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/408).
    * Works on Macs with old chipsets [#398](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/398), [#982](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/982).
    * Better error reporting from missing backend [#1180](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1180), [#880](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/880), 
    * New API for progress reporting during cell evaluation [#910](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/910).
    * New API for fullscreen dashboards [#1025](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1025).
    * New API for reflection (access to other cells source code and results) and control (cell evaluation can trigger evaluation of other cells).
    * Standard output and error output now appear below the cell that produced them instead of in a unified panel [#667](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/667), [#937](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/937).
    * Add tutorial for loading external Javascript libraries, in particular p5.js [#1176](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1176).
    * Allow sharing and saving `<canvas>` elements [#1075](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1075).
    * Handle installation and user paths with spaces [#931](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/931).
    * Fix Javascript injection problem on shared notebooks [#862](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/862).
    * New View menu item "close all sections" [#872](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/872).
    * Upload notebooks with native file dialog or drag-and-drop [#830](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/830), [#857](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/857), [#1116](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1116).
    * Improved Language Manager UI.
    * Use scss to improve modularity of styles [#1071](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1071).
    * Support ipynb section headings during import [#1015](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1015).
    * Subsections numbered from 1 instead of 0 [#629](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/629).
    * Groovy evaluation is interruptible [#560](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/560).
    * Add progress indicator to sharing [#383](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/383).
    * UI for tagging cells [#403](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/403).
    * R plots made with ggplot2 work on Firefox [#987](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/987)
    * On Windows find R via the registry instead of the PATH [#1178](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1178).
    * Improved file open and save dialogs [#904](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/904), [#1016](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1016), [#1017](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1017), [#1061](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1061), [#1158](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1158), [#1159](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1159), [#1161](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1161).
    * Massive UI polish [#672](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/672), [#673](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/673), [#747](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/747), [#772](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/772), [#819](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/819), [#854](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/854), [#856](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/856), [#874](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/874), [#902](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/902), [#906](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/906), [#968](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/968), [#970](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/970), [#972](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/972), [#990](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/990), [#1027](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1027), [#1045](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1045), [#1047](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1047), [#1053](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1053), [#1062](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1062), [#1070](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1070), [#1119](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1119), [#1130](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1130), [#1139](https://github.com/twosigma/beaker-notebook/issues/1139).

